name: ASUS ROG Zephyrus G16
description:
Introducing the UltraBook Pro Series

Where performance meets elegance. Experience the future of computing with our most advanced laptop series designed for professionals, creators, and innovators.

Configure Your Laptop View Specifications

Why Choose UltraBook Pro?

Built for the modern professional who demands excellence in every aspect of their computing experience.

Blazing Performance

12th Gen Intel Core i7 processor with 32GB DDR5 RAM and RTX 4060 graphics for seamless multitasking and content creation.

Stunning 4K OLED Display

15.6" 4K OLED touchscreen with 100% DCI-P3 color accuracy and 400 nits brightness for professional-grade visuals.

All-Day Battery Life

Up to 18 hours of battery life with rapid 65W USB-C charging. Work unplugged from dawn to dusk.

Enterprise Security

Biometric fingerprint reader, TPM 2.0 chip, and Windows Hello facial recognition for ultimate security.

Future-Ready Connectivity

Wi-Fi 6E, Bluetooth 5.3, Thunderbolt 4 ports, and 5G optional for staying connected anywhere.

Premium Support & Warranty

3-year premium warranty with 24/7 tech support and on-site service for business customers.

Complete Professional Package

Every UltraBook Pro comes with a premium leather sleeve, wireless mouse, USB-C dock, and 1-year Microsoft 365 subscription.

Perfect for Every Professional

Business Executives

Lightweight design, enterprise security, and all-day battery life make it perfect for boardroom presentations and international travel.

  • Advanced video conferencing capabilities
  • Instant wake and Windows Hello login
  • Military-grade durability testing

Creative Professionals

4K OLED display with 100% color accuracy and powerful RTX graphics for photo editing, video production, and 3D design.

  • Adobe Creative Suite optimized
  • Pantone validated display
  • Hardware-accelerated ray tracing

Software Developers

Powerful processing, ample RAM, and fast SSD storage handle large codebases, virtual machines, and development environments.

  • Docker and Kubernetes ready
  • Linux compatibility certified
  • Multiple 4K external display support
